The paper discusses the optimization of graph computation and the partitioning of graph databases, which are topics related to database systems (cs.DB), social networks (cs.SI), data structures (cs.DS), system and control (cs.SY), and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). However, since the paper focuses on the evaluation of partitioning algorithms and their impact on database performance, cs.DB is the most likely sub-category.
